reviews.text: Escape into Yau Man Street a small street beside McDonald in Quarry Bay, you will find the restaurant on the right behind #116 bus terminus. The real Thai restaurant runs by the Thai couple. The male is in charge in the kitchen with his sister and the wife is taking care the service customers herself. The food is real Thai eatery you can have in Thailand. If you have never tried this place, got to hurry up. As its rent will expire end of 2019. They may have to close down cuz the annual Increment of rent. Very unfortunate that small owner will not be able to survive due to escalating high rent annually.
Great lunch place with good prices. Highly recommend the green curry chicken with rice.
